title: Kolima
author: camokool
pages:
#- THE PEACE TREATY OF /POL/ & AEROTHERS

This legislation acts as a peace treatment and a non-aggression alliance between both
/Pol/ynesia and the player AEROTHERS, and his/her factions council in the following laws:

#- ------Start of legislation----

1. All NON ‘peaceful’ affairs by any players of either faction will result in pearling.

2. /Pol/ynesia will protect any land surrounding Kolima from any deemed a 'Channer'
#- 3. No channer, or /Pol/ynesian will enter will enter Kolima without permission from Aerothers until word and clearing from Aerothers, and or a representative of his/her council, with exception of Claus 2, /Pol/ynesia will have clearance to enter
#- territories if the need to serve and protect arises.

4. Both parties will hold to their respectful territories and only interact in a peaceful or profitable manner.


#- 5. Aerothers will have full control over Kolima and it’s respected boundaries in order to preserve the township.

6. In respect to land that is being held, /Pol/ynesia has a small farming outpost on Kolima lands.
#- With permission of the Aerothers, Kolima will be subdivided. Due to Clause 2 /Pol/ynesia will provide protection of the township (Kolima) in order to continue operations

---END OF LEGISLATION---

#- Written by Camokool ﻿Minister of Architecture, Diplomacy, & Law


